{"tid":2149683,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過全身嘅神經有不明原因嘅痛？","createTime":"2020-08-10T13:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T15:23:20.000Z","uid":221696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1bebf465d7eeee37c6dd052c525a4bd0d5fcd705","tid":2149683,"uid":221696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:51:00.000Z","msg":"有時成身會無端端一個位置神經痛，嗰種感覺有時好似俾刀割、俾嘢咬、俾電電親咁。多數痛嘅位置四肢、頸、塊面。<br />\n<br />\n之前試過因為呢個問題去睇醫生，醫生可能估我係情緒問題，開咗啲鎮靜劑之類嘅藥，但上網見到啲藥好多副作用就無食到。<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲打有試過同樣問題？我應該點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596397d8903960d3e836c996b1843a4886c53737","tid":2149683,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:51:52.000Z","msg":"同一個位？"},{"pid":"d421c1ebac52291ee103f9642dbfe17c72533759","tid":2149683,"uid":121855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:58:51.000Z","msg":"生蛇！"},{"pid":"8869ca2b5b0f258b1259a58e46e975434268adb0","tid":2149683,"uid":271250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:01:47.000Z","msg":"有。，響手指頭位痛，好似突然被針扎咁，1～5秒痛楚會消失，所以都無理到。"},{"pid":"5de510e1dd70b53ee0f0d2f2fdcd109973041f32","tid":2149683,"uid":311728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:06:09.000Z","msg":"有 試過係背脊下背大概腰嗰位痛 係突然間咁痛 唔識形容點痛 但係喺訓落床都無用嗰隻 痛左幾個月之後到而家都無痛過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5583fc4320cbdadbf30041b90be4ca3bb62ca24","tid":2149683,"uid":236855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:09:47.000Z","msg":"太大壓力有機會會咁樣<br />\n放鬆下一排都係咁就可能再睇專科睇下啲神經線"},{"pid":"d52e3b559b02526d3b0175dcbbae4c68604106d1","tid":2149683,"uid":188411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:11:40.000Z","msg":"食維他命b12"},{"pid":"399b7f76f5ccbbe64b3f99e2f1b93354245b74d3","tid":2149683,"uid":113189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:30:53.000Z","msg":"雖然唔知醫生開左咩鎮靜劑比你 不過有啲同時係精神科藥物係可以作為鬆弛劑舒緩到腰痛 我都試過腰痛睇醫生開左比我啊 但醫生講明只係for短期用 劑量亦因為針對唔同問題而唔同 所以你網上搵到啲好嚴重嘅副作用都未必發生係你身上<br />\n如果你試咗其他方法都幫你唔到不如試返醫生開比你啲鎮靜劑 萬一真係有副作用令你好唔舒服 其實都可以停左佢or搵返醫生商量啊 試多個方法都好過無從入手 拖得越耐仲辛苦啊<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d66aa7f58a54bd58b2e21ca19bd2348499285dd","tid":2149683,"uid":4789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"內絡必安？"},{"pid":"fc67cd4c1943396b7dff17f59314e3932cffc7f3","tid":2149683,"uid":221696,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"596397d8903960d3e836c996b1843a4886c53737","tid":2149683,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:51:52.000Z","msg":"同一個位？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T18:32:34.000Z","msg":"唔係同一個位，每次痛嘅位都唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d01a6c51224650d1037a73df9c4182567b60634","tid":2149683,"uid":221696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8869ca2b5b0f258b1259a58e46e975434268adb0","tid":2149683,"uid":271250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:01:47.000Z","msg":"有。，響手指頭位痛，好似突然被針扎咁，1～5秒痛楚會消失，所以都無理到。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T18:33:28.000Z","msg":"巴打淨係手指頭痛？"},{"pid":"5ce846e2af2b4b1821e11d23eb1c7ee3e86ceb0b","tid":2149683,"uid":221696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5de510e1dd70b53ee0f0d2f2fdcd109973041f32","tid":2149683,"uid":311728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T14:06:09.000Z","msg":"有 試過係背脊下背大概腰嗰位痛 係突然間咁痛 唔識形容點痛 但係喺訓落床都無用嗰隻 痛左幾個月之後到而家都無痛過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T18:34:14.000Z","msg":"有無去睇醫生？定佢自然就唔痛？"},{"pid":"f335b67c8620c8207f1f10a17f975f33ca524088","tid":2149683,"uid":311728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ce846e2af2b4b1821e11d23eb1c7ee3e86ceb0b","tid":2149683,"uid":221696,"li